{"word":"H41 - אֲבִינָדָב - ʼĂbîynâdâb - ab-ee-naw-dawb' - Abinadab","slug":"H41","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">אֲבִינָדָב</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>ʼĂbîynâdâb"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>ab-ee-naw-dawb'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Abinadab"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"Original: <b><he>אבינדב</he></b> <p />Transliteration: <b>'ăbı̂ynâdâb</b> <p />Phonetic: <b>ab-ee-naw-dawb'</b> <p class=\"bdb_def\"><b>BDB Definition</b>:</p> Abinadab = \"my father is noble\" or \" my father is willing\" <ol><li>a man of Gibeah who sheltered the ark</li><li>second son of Jesse, David's older brother</li><li>a son of Saul, slain with him by the Philistines</li></ol> <p />Origin: from <a href=\"#/H1\">H1</a> and <a href=\"#/H5068\">H5068</a> <p />TWOT entry: None <p />Part(s) of speech: Proper Name Masculine "},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1\">H1</a>, <a href=\"#/H21\">H21</a>, <a href=\"#/H22\">H22</a>, <a href=\"#/H23\">H23</a>, <a href=\"#/H26\">H26</a>, <a href=\"#/H27\">H27</a>, <a href=\"#/H28\">H28</a>, <a href=\"#/H29\">H29</a>, <a href=\"#/H30\">H30</a>, <a href=\"#/H31\">H31</a>, <a href=\"#/H32\">H32</a>, <a href=\"#/H33\">H33</a>, <a href=\"#/H36\">H36</a>, <a href=\"#/H37\">H37</a>, <a href=\"#/H372\">H372</a>, <a href=\"#/H373\">H373</a>, <a href=\"#/H38\">H38</a>, <a href=\"#/H39\">H39</a>, <a href=\"#/H40\">H40</a>, <a href=\"#/H42\">H42</a>, <a href=\"#/H43\">H43</a>, <a href=\"#/H44\">H44</a>, <a href=\"#/H45\">H45</a>, <a href=\"#/H48\">H48</a>, <a href=\"#/H49\">H49</a>, <a href=\"#/H50\">H50</a>, <a href=\"#/H51\">H51</a>, <a href=\"#/H52\">H52</a>, <a href=\"#/H53\">H53</a>, <a href=\"#/H54\">H54</a>, <a href=\"#/H74\">H74</a>, <a href=\"#/H85\">H85</a>, <a href=\"#/H87\">H87</a>"}]}